carbonenginejs/reader-hlsl
==========================

A pure-JavaScript reader for CCP's Tr2 compiled effect container format
(`.sm_hi` / `.sm_lo` / `.sm_depth` bodies): the permutation axes, technique
and pass tables, and per-stage constant/resource/sampler metadata that make
up one compiled Carbon/Trinity effect resource.

Contains no CCP code. The container layout was recovered through clean-room
analysis of compiled effect files and is described here in the reader's own
words; no CCP source, tooling, or proprietary documentation is included in
this repository. Shader bytecode bodies are kept as opaque bytes
(`CjsShaderBytecode`) — this package does not decode DXBC/HLSL bytecode.

